						<summary>

						<p>On a stone set up in a field called Rājanna-chēnu in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 154[9], Prabhava, Jyeśhṭha, śu. 15, corresponding to 1627 A.D., May 19, Saturday.</p>						

						<p>Records the gift of land at Kaṁbhaṁpāḍu to a certain Rāmarāju Śaṅkana by Veligōṭi Narasappa, who held the <hi rend="italic">ijārati</hi> of the village.</p>						

